      <tr><td>Capacity</td><td>28 GPM on Diesel Fuel</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Motor</td><td>460V / 3Ph – 7.5 HP Motor</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Skid Size</td><td>5' x 4' x 6' (H)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Weight</td><td>~ 2,500 Lbs</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Power</td><td>460 VAC Power - 50 A Circuit</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Water</td><td>Filtered, Potable through 3/4" Line @ 5 GPM and 30 psig</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Air</td><td>100 psig, filtered, dry air</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Included options</td><td>PC Touch-Screen Control System and Water Harness</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p><em><strong>In some cases, Dolphin Centrifuge can accommodate long-term rental requirements by building a skid for specific customer applications.</strong></em></p>

  <!-- MAPX 210 Disc Stack Centrifuge Rental -->
  <h2 id="mapx210">MAPX 210 Disc Stack Centrifuge Rental</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
    <div class="md:w-1/2">
      <p><strong><a href="/alfa-laval-whpx-510-centrifuge/" class="text-navy hover:text-gold transition-colors">Alfa Laval MAPX 210</a> 42 GPM Self-Cleaning, Disc Stack, Rental Centrifuge</strong></p>
      <h3>Applications</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/diesel-centrifuge/"><strong>Diesel Fuel</strong></a></li>
        <li><a href="/lube-oil-centrifuge/"><strong>Engine Oil</strong></a></li>
        <li><a href="/hydraulic-oil-centrifuge/"><strong>Hydraulic Oil</strong></a></li>
        <li><a href="/crude-oil-centrifuge/"><strong>Light Crude Oil</strong></a></li>
        <li><a href="/waste-oil-centrifuge/"><strong>Waste Oil – Used Oil</strong></a></li>
        <li><a href="/oil-centrifuge/"><strong>Industrial Oils</strong></a></li>
        <li><a href="/wvo-centrifuge-separator/"><strong>WVO, UCO, Grease Trap/Yellow Grease</strong></a></li>
        <li>and other 3-phase separation with &lt;5% solids (v/v).</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/2">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/images/disc-stack-centrifuge-rental/Alfa-Laval-42-GPM-Self-Cleaning-Rental-Centrifuge.webp" alt="Alfa Laval 42 GPM Self Cleaning Rental Centrifuge" width="600" height="600" class="rounded-xl" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <p><em><strong>If you have simple, routine questions: We have condensed our 40+ years of disc-stack centrifuge experience into <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-faq/">101 Frequently Asked Questions about Disc Stack Centrifuges!</a></strong></em></p>

  <h3>MAPX 210 Specifications</h3>
  <table>
