      <tr><td>Weight</td><td>~ 3,500 Lbs</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Power</td><td>460 VAC Power - 50 A Circuit</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Water</td><td>Filtered, Potable through 3/4" Line @ 5 GPM and 30 psig</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Air</td><td>100 psig, filtered, dry air</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Included options</td><td>Sludge Tank, Sludge Pump, Feed Pump w/ VFD Control, PLC Touch-Screen Control System, etc.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <!-- Additive Content -->
  <h2 id="why-rent">Why Rent a Disc Stack Centrifuge?</h2>
  <p>Purchasing an industrial <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">disc stack centrifuge</a> is a significant capital investment. Renting gives you immediate access to high-performance separation equipment without the upfront cost, allowing you to validate your process, cover temporary needs, or bridge the gap while your own unit is being <a href="/industrial-disc-centrifuge-repair/">repaired or rebuilt</a>.</p>
  <p>Every rental centrifuge in our fleet has been fully rebuilt in our Warren, Michigan facility and tested on our high-speed test stand before deployment. You receive a production-ready machine — not a worn-out demo unit.</p>

  <h2 id="rental-apps">Rental Applications</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Pilot Testing:</strong> Validate centrifuge performance on your specific fluid before committing to a purchase. Pair with our <a href="/industrial-centrifuge-sample-testing/">sample testing service</a> for lab-scale data first</li>
    <li><strong>Temporary Capacity:</strong> Cover seasonal demand spikes, plant turnarounds, or emergency spill response without purchasing additional equipment</li>
    <li><strong>Trial Before Purchase:</strong> Run the centrifuge in your facility for weeks or months before deciding to buy</li>
    <li><strong>Bridge During Repair:</strong> Keep your process running while your own centrifuge is in our shop for rebuild</li>
    <li><strong>Project-Based Work:</strong> Short-duration contracts, remediation projects, or construction dewatering</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="models">Available Rental Models</h2>
  <p>Our <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-applications/">disc stack rental fleet</a> includes self-cleaning DMPX-series separators covering a wide range of flow rates and applications:</p>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Model</th><th>Type</th><th>Flow Rate</th><th>Typical Applications</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>DMPX-010</td><td>Self-Cleaning</td><td>Up to 8 GPM</td><td>Small-volume oil, fuel, biodiesel</td></tr>
      <tr><td>DMPX-014</td><td>Self-Cleaning</td><td>Up to 16 GPM</td><td>Waste oil, lube oil, diesel</td></tr>
      <tr><td>DMPX-028</td><td>Self-Cleaning</td><td>Up to 28 GPM</td><td>Fuel oil, process water, food-grade</td></tr>
      <tr><td>DMPX-042</td><td>Self-Cleaning</td><td>Up to 47 GPM</td><td>Large-volume oil, wastewater, marine</td></tr>
      <tr><td>DMPX-070</td><td>Self-Cleaning</td><td>Up to 72 GPM</td><td>High-volume industrial, refinery</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p>Manual-clean DMB-series separators are also available for applications with low solids loading. Contact us to discuss which model fits your process.</p>

  <h2 id="included">What's Included in a Rental</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Fully Rebuilt Centrifuge:</strong> Every rental unit is rebuilt to OEM specifications with new <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-parts/">bearings, seals, and O-rings</a></li>
    <li><strong>Complete System:</strong> Centrifuge, feed pump, motor, starter, and basic piping connections</li>
    <li><strong>Operating Manual:</strong> Process-specific setup guide and recommended operating parameters</li>
    <li><strong>Technical Support:</strong> Phone and email support from our engineers during the rental period</li>
    <li><strong>Startup Assistance:</strong> Remote or on-site commissioning support available</li>
    <li><strong>Spare Parts Kit:</strong> Basic consumables included for the rental duration</li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Mid-Page CTA -->
  <div class="bg-gold/10 border-l-4 border-gold rounded-r-xl p-5 my-8 not-prose">
    <p class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Ready to Rent a Disc Stack Centrifuge?</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-light mb-3">Dolphin Centrifuge ships fully rebuilt DMPX-series separators nationwide. Contact us for current availability, pricing, and application guidance.</p>
    <a href="/contact-for-alfa-laval-centrifuges/" class="inline-block bg-gold text-white font-semibold px-5 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gold/90 transition-colors text-sm">Get Rental Pricing</a>
  </div>

  <h2 id="comparison">Rental vs. Purchase</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Factor</th><th>Rental</th><th>Purchase</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Upfront Cost</td><td>Low monthly payments</td><td>Full capital expenditure</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Commitment</td><td>Flexible — return when done</td><td>Long-term ownership</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Maintenance</td><td>Included during rental</td><td>Owner responsibility</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Best For</td><td>Testing, short-term, temporary needs</td><td>Continuous, long-term operation</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p><strong>Rent-to-Own:</strong> Rental payments can apply toward purchase price.</p>

  <h2 id="terms">Rental Terms</h2>
  <p>We offer flexible rental terms tailored to your project timeline:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Short-Term:</strong> 1–3 months for pilot testing, emergency response, or project work</li>
    <li><strong>Long-Term:</strong> 6–12+ months with reduced monthly rates</li>
    <li><strong>Rent-to-Own:</strong> Apply rental payments toward eventual purchase</li>
    <li><strong>Shipping:</strong> We arrange freight to and from your facility anywhere in the continental U.S.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Looking for a decanter centrifuge instead? See our <a href="/decanter-centrifuge-rental/">decanter centrifuge rental program</a> for NX and G2-series units.</p>

  <FAQ items={faqItems} />

</ApplicationLayout>
